Class BotCore

    public class BotCore

    A bot core providing basic minimal functionality for connecting to an IRC server.

       java.lang.String real,
       java.lang.String[] chans,
       boolean beanshell,
       boolean jython,
       boolean jacl)
        Starts the bot core.
        Parameters:
        beanshell - True if the bot is to run the beanshell script handler, otherwise false.
        jython - True if the bot is to run the jython script handler, otherwise false.
        jacl - True if the bot is to run the jacl script handler, otherwise false.
        nicknames - An array of nicknames to use
        chans - An array of channel names to join
        host - Hostname of server
        port - Port number to connect to
        user - User name
        real - Real name
